    public class CardFragment
extends android.support.v4.app.Fragment
    A fragment representing a list of Items.

    Activities containing this fragment MUST implement the CardFragment.OnListFragmentInteractionListener interface.

    • 嵌套类概要

      嵌套类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      static interface  CardFragment.OnListFragmentInteractionListener
      This interface must be implemented by activities that contain this fragment to allow an interaction in this fragment to be communicated to the activity and potentially other fragments contained in that activity.
